      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A conference of the representa-.\ntives of the Great Northern, the\no. r. C N. and the Spokane & In.\nternaticnal railway met yesterday\nin the Office of d. G. Corbin in the\nHyde block, for the purpose of con.\nsiderlng grade separation in the\nlower part of the Fifth ward. TIE\nquestion of a passenger depot to be\nused jointly by the two lines was\ntaken up. The conference ended\nwith no positive agreement, but all\ninterests worked in harmony."
